General.Name: KSH Holdings Limited
General.Description: KSH Holdings Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a construction builder and contractor for public and private sectors. The company operates through three segments: Construction, Property Development and Investment, and Corporate and Others. It constructs residential, commercial, hospitality, and mixed-use development projects; rents and sells properties; and operates hotels. The company operates in Singapore, the People's Republic of China, Malaysia, Bhutan, Japan, Australia, and the United Kingdom. KSH Holdings Limited was incorporated in 1979 and is based in Singapore.
